### Criar task
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Correlation-Id: 3f5d5a34-7d74-4f6c-b91d-9a1dbb2c7d3f

{
  "key": "TSK-123",
  "title": "Implementar /login com Correlation-Id",
  "dodPolicyId": "default-java-service",
  "assignee": "vinicius",
  "labels": ["security","observability"],
  "correlationId": "3f5d5a34-7d74-4f6c-b91d-9a1dbb2c7d3f"
}

### Listar tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks

### Detalhar task (troque {id})
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks/{id}

### Transicionar estado
PATCH http://localhost:8080/tasks/{id}/state
Content-Type: application/json

{ "state": "VERIFICATION" }

### Webhook: PR merged
POST http://localhost:8080/webhooks/github
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "gh-evt-123",
  "type": "PR_MERGED",
  "repo": "org/app",
  "branch": "main",
  "pr": 42,
  "taskKey": "TSK-123"
}

